existing_features.title:
Create a file named `.ic-assets.json` in the top-level frontend canister directory (`frontend/`, same level as `public/`) with exactly the following JSON content (including the array and fields) so that the `.well-known` directory is not ignored during asset publishing:

[
  {
    "match": ".well-known",
    "ignore": false
  }
]

After this change, the deployed frontend canister must publicly serve the existing verification file at `/.well-known/ic-domains`.
